<DATELINE>PARIS (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Remember the raincoat that President Bush so
generously gave away to an elderly woman in a rainstorm in Budapest,
Hungary? Well, it wasn't his.
   Bush's wife, Barbara, said today the raincoat belonged to a
Secret Service agent who was accompanying the president to an
