astronaut uses of what sort of shoes he, or she, wears,'' said
agency spokesman Bill Jones.``If we are successful, this guy will go
up looking like a racing driver!''
   Britain has to raise $25.6 million by commercial sponsorship,
much of which will go to the total $51.2 million cost.
