early 1990, with completion about ten months later.
   There were no new Tennessee franchises announced. Lee Beaman,
president of Beaman Automotive Group in Nashville, is the only
Tennessee dealership awarded a franchise so far.
   Saturn will offer two four-door models and one two-door car in
the subcompact or compact segment of the market. GM officials have
said the car will compete with imports.
