<TEXT>
   Share prices rose slightly Thursday on the London
stock exchange in tentative, volatile trading.
   The Financial Time 100-share index rose 1.3 points, or .06
percent, to close at 2,258.0.
   The narrower FT 30-share index rose 9.7 points at 1,868.0. The
